menu.full_description: Classic Bavarian white sausage made from finely minced veal and pork back bacon, flavored with parsley, lemon, mace, onions, ginger, and cardamom. Typically served warm with sweet mustard and freshly baked pretzels.
menu.special_notes: Available even after 12 PM, rare in Munich

menu.name: Münchner Schnitzel
menu.short_description: Breaded pork schnitzel with mustard marinade and fried potatoes
menu.full_description: Traditional Munich-style schnitzel made from pork, marinated in mustard, breaded and fried to a golden crisp. Served with fried potatoes. The mustard marinade is subtle, and the dish is a classic Bavarian main course.

menu.name: Wirtshausgulasch
menu.short_description: Spicy Bavarian-style beef goulash
menu.full_description: Hearty Bavarian goulash made with tender beef chunks, slow-cooked in a rich and slightly spicy sauce with paprika and onions. Served with traditional sides such as bread or potatoes.

menu.name: Spargel mit Wacholdaschinken
menu.short_description: Seasonal asparagus wrapped in juniper-smoked ham
menu.full_description: Fresh seasonal white asparagus wrapped in juniper-flavored smoked ham, served with traditional Bavarian sides and a herb butter or sauce. A springtime specialty highlighting local ingredients.

menu.name: Bärlauchspätzle mit Schweinemedaillons
menu.short_description: Wild garlic spätzle with pork medallions
menu.full_description: Homemade spätzle (soft egg noodles) infused with wild garlic, served alongside tender pork medallions. A flavorful seasonal dish combining fresh herbs and quality meat.

menu.name: St. Martins-Gans
menu.short_description: Roast goose traditionally served for St. Martin's Day
menu.full_description: Traditional Bavarian roast goose served with red cabbage, dumplings, and gravy. A festive dish typically enjoyed during the St. Martin's Day celebrations in autumn.

menu.name: Kürbispflanzerl mit Ratatouille-Gemüse und Kräuterdip
menu.short_description: Pumpkin patties with ratatouille vegetables and herb dip
menu.full_description: Vegetarian pumpkin patties served with a side of ratatouille-style stewed vegetables and a fresh herb dip. A seasonal dish highlighting autumn flavors and fresh herbs.

menu.name: Chili & Cheese Nuggets
menu.short_description: Knusprige Nuggets mit schmelzendem Käse und scharfen Chilis in Panade
menu.full_description: Knusprige Panade umhüllt Nuggets, die mit schmelzendem Cheese und feurigen Chilis kombiniert sind, für einen besonders würzigen Genuss. Perfektes Fingerfood für Liebhaber von scharfem Geschmack.
menu.special_notes: Besonders würzig durch Kombination von Käse und Chili

menu.name: Crusty Chicken
menu.short_description: Knusprig panierte Chicken Fingers im Sesam Bun mit Tomaten, Salat und Mayonnaise
menu.full_description: Knusprig-panierte Chicken Fingers (95 g) serviert im klassischen Sesam Brötchen, verfeinert mit fruchtigen Tomaten, knackigem Salat und cremiger Mayonnaise. Ein Klassiker für alle, die Chicken lieben.

menu.name: Süßkartoffel-Pommes
menu.short_description: Knusprige Süßkartoffel-Pommes mit süßlichem und herzhaftem Geschmack
menu.full_description: Gold-orangene Süßkartoffel-Pommes mit knuspriger Kruste und weichem Inneren, die durch ihren süßlichen und dennoch herzhaften Geschmack überzeugen. Perfekte Beilage zu Burgern.

menu.name: Cheesy Hot Fries
menu.short_description: Knusprige Pommes mit schmelzendem Käse und feurigen Jalapeños
menu.full_description: Knusprige Pommes Frites, überzogen mit einem schmelzenden Cheese Topping und verfeinert mit feurigen Jalapeños. Ideal als Beilage oder als scharfer Snack zwischendurch.

menu.name: Onion Rings
menu.short_description: Frittierte Zwiebelringe in klassischem Bierteig, knusprig und goldbraun
menu.full_description: Acht geschnittene Zwiebelringe, paniert in einer goldbraunen, knusprigen Bierteig-Panade und frittiert. Ein klassischer Burgerbegleiter, der auch als Snack oder zum Salat hervorragend passt.

menu.name: Hamburger
menu.short_description: Klassischer Hamburger mit 125g Rindfleisch, Salat, Tomaten, Gurken und Zwiebeln im Sesam Brötchen
menu.full_description: Der absolute Klassiker unter den Burgern: 125 g frisch gegrilltes Classic Beef auf einem Sesam Brötchen, belegt mit knackigem Salat, fruchtigen Tomaten, sauren Gurken und Zwiebeln. Ein zeitloser Genuss.

menu.name: Cheese Burger
menu.short_description: Hamburger mit geschmolzenem Emmentaler Käse, Salat, Tomaten und Zwiebeln
menu.full_description: Klassischer Hamburger mit 125 g Classic Beef Patty, Sesam Brötchen, frischem Salat, Tomaten, Zwiebeln und geschmolzenem Emmentaler Käse. Verfeinert mit einer einzigartigen Chipotle-South-West-Sauce für ein besonderes Aroma.

menu.name: Bacon BBQ
menu.short_description: Burger mit 125g Classic Beef, knusprigem Bacon, BBQ-Sauce, Salat, Tomaten, Gurken und Zwiebeln
menu.full_description: Herzhafter Burger mit 125 g frisch gegrilltem Classic Beef Patty, knusprigem Bacon, würziger BBQ-Sauce, Salat, Tomaten, sauren Gurken und Zwiebeln auf einem Sesam Brötchen. Ein Burger für echte Fleischliebhaber.

menu.name: Big Angus Cheese
menu.short_description: Burger mit 150g gegrilltem Angus Beef, Bacon, Bergkäse, Salat, Gurke, Zwiebeln und Tomaten
menu.full_description: Premium-Burger mit 150 g perfekt gegrilltem Angus Beef Patty, knusprigem Bacon, würzigem Bergkäse, frischem Salat, Gurke, roten Zwiebeln und Tomaten auf einem Brötchen. Für alle, die geschmacklich hoch hinaus wollen.

menu.name: Chil'n'Cheese Burger
menu.short_description: Burger mit Classic Beef, doppelt Käsesauce und feurigen Jalapeños
menu.full_description: Burger mit 125 g Classic Beef Patty, Sesam Brötchen, Zwiebeln, Salat, doppelter Käsesauce und feurigen Jalapeños. Für alle, die es gerne pikant und würzig mögen.

menu.name: Grilled Chicken Burger
menu.short_description: Gegrilltes Hühnchen mit Bergkäse, Rucola, roter Paprika und Chipotle-Sauce im Rustico Brötchen
menu.full_description: Frisch gegrilltes Chicken Patty serviert im herzhaften Rustico Brötchen mit kräftigem Bergkäse, nussigem Rucola, roter Paprika, Chipotle-Sauce, Curry-Sauce und Ketchup. Eine leckere Alternative zum klassischen Beef Burger.

menu.name: Meatfree Crunchy Burger
menu.short_description: Würzig paniertes Meatfree Crunchy Patty mit Tomaten, Salat und veganer Mayonnaise im Sesam Bun
menu.full_description: Fleischlose Alternative mit würzig paniertem Meatfree Crunchy Patty (120 g), fruchtigen Tomaten, knackigem Salat und veganer Mayonnaise im Sesam Brötchen. Für Veganer und Vegetarier geeignet.

menu.name: Fingerfood-Box
menu.short_description: Mix aus Chicken Wings, Nuggets, Chicken Fingers oder Cheesy Wedges und Chili & Cheese Nuggets
menu.full_description: Genieße drei Fingerfood-Spezialitäten deiner Wahl zum Sparpreis. Auswahl aus Chicken Wings, Nuggets, Chicken Fingers, Cheesy Wedges und doppelt Chili & Cheese Nuggets. Perfekt zum Teilen oder als Snack.

menu.name: Pfefferbeißer, Salami, Bacon, Hot Smoked Ham, Stammhaus-Beersausage
menu.short_description: Assorted traditional Bavarian sausages and cured meats served with horseradish, red onions, gherkins, and garden radish
menu.full_description: A classic Bavarian appetizer platter featuring Pfefferbeißer (pepper sausages), salami, bacon, hot smoked ham, and the house specialty Stammhaus-Beersausage, garnished with freshly sliced horseradish, red onions, gherkins, and garden radish to complement the rich flavors.

menu.name: Augustiner Cheese Platter
menu.short_description: Selection of Bavarian cheeses with garnishes including red onions, gherkins, and tomato
menu.full_description: A cheese platter featuring Allgäuer mountain cheese, Emmenthaler, butter-caraway cheese, Gouda, Romadur, and Obatzda, served with traditional garnishes such as red onions, gherkins, and fresh tomato slices, offering a rich variety of textures and flavors typical of the region.

menu.name: Appetizer Beard – Salmon
menu.short_description: Smoked matjes, grilled scampis, mild smoked fjord salmon with horseradish cream, grilled antipasti vegetables, baby mozzarella, balsamico glaze
menu.full_description: A refined appetizer combining tender smoked matjes herring with housewife sauce, grilled scampis, mild smoked fjord salmon topped with horseradish cream, accompanied by grilled antipasti vegetables and baby mozzarella finished with a balsamico glaze, offering a balanced mix of smoky, creamy, and fresh flavors.

menu.name: Courgettes Cream Soup with Herbs and a Fried Scampi Spit
menu.short_description: Creamy courgette soup flavored with herbs, served with a fried scampi skewer
menu.full_description: A smooth and creamy courgette (zucchini) soup delicately seasoned with fresh herbs, accompanied by a skewer of crispy fried scampi, combining a light vegetable base with a crunchy seafood element for a balanced starter.

menu.name: Old Port Stewed Ox Cheeks with Glazed Carrot Vegetables and Potato-Leek Purée
menu.short_description: Slow-cooked ox cheeks in old port wine with glazed carrots and creamy potato-leek purée
menu.full_description: Tender ox cheeks stewed slowly in rich old port wine, served with sweet glazed carrot vegetables and a smooth potato-leek purée, delivering a hearty and flavorful main course typical of Bavarian comfort cuisine.

menu.name: Caramelized Kaiserschmarrn
menu.short_description: Traditional Bavarian shredded pancake caramelized and served in a reindeer pan
menu.full_description: A classic Bavarian dessert consisting of fluffy shredded pancakes caramelized to a golden brown, traditionally served in a reindeer-shaped pan (Reinderl), often accompanied by fruit compote or powdered sugar.
menu.special_notes: Served in a traditional reindeer pan (Reinderl)

menu.name: Fresh Bavarian White Sausage, Regensburger Sausage and Frankfurters with Meatballs
menu.short_description: Variety of Bavarian sausages and meatballs served fresh from the pan
menu.full_description: A hearty plate featuring freshly cooked Bavarian white sausages, Regensburger sausages, Frankfurters, and pan-fried meatballs, representing traditional Bavarian meat specialties.

menu.name: Crispy Pork Roast with Dark Beer Sauce
menu.short_description: Roasted pork with crispy skin served with a rich dark beer sauce
menu.full_description: Traditional Bavarian crispy pork roast featuring crackling skin, served with a flavorful dark beer sauce that enhances the savory meat, a classic dish in Munich's beer halls.

menu.name: Munich Meat Loaf with Sauerkraut and Bacon
menu.short_description: Traditional Munich meat loaf served with sauerkraut cooked with bacon
menu.full_description: A savory Munich-style meat loaf accompanied by sauerkraut enhanced with bacon pieces, combining hearty meat flavors with the tangy and smoky notes of the sauerkraut.

menu.name: Obatzda with Onions and Emmentaler on a Piece
menu.short_description: Traditional Bavarian cheese spread Obatzda served with onions and a slice of Emmentaler cheese
menu.full_description: A classic Bavarian appetizer featuring Obatzda, a creamy cheese spread made from aged Camembert mixed with butter and spices, served with raw onions and a slice of Emmentaler cheese, perfect for pairing with pretzels or bread.
menu.special_notes: Often served with pretzels on request

menu.name: Bavarian Farmers Chicken with Munich Meat Loaf, Glazed Knuckle of Veal, Bread Dumpling, Sauerkraut with Bacon, Red Cabbage and Seasonal Vegetables
menu.short_description: Hearty Bavarian platter with chicken, meat loaf, veal knuckle, bread dumplings, sauerkraut, red cabbage, and seasonal vegetables
menu.full_description: A substantial Bavarian main course featuring a roasted farmers chicken, traditional Munich meat loaf, glazed knuckle of veal, served alongside bread dumplings, sauerkraut cooked with bacon, red cabbage, and fresh vegetables in season, showcasing a variety of classic regional flavors.

menu.name: Homemade Bavarian Cream with Raspberry Sauce
menu.short_description: Smooth Bavarian cream dessert served with fresh raspberry sauce
menu.full_description: A delicate and creamy Bavarian cream dessert, homemade and served with a fresh raspberry sauce that adds a fruity and slightly tart contrast to the sweet, silky cream.

menu.name: Apple and Cream Cheese Strudel with Delicate Vanilla Sauce
menu.short_description: Warm apple and cream cheese strudel served with a smooth vanilla sauce
menu.full_description: A freshly baked strudel filled with tart apples and creamy cheese, served warm and accompanied by a delicate vanilla sauce that enhances the dessert's sweetness and richness, a beloved Bavarian treat.

menu.name: Currywurst mit Pommes frites mit Currysauce
menu.short_description: Sliced sausage served with French fries and curry sauce
menu.full_description: Traditional German currywurst, a steamed then fried pork sausage sliced and topped with a tangy curry-flavored ketchup sauce, served alongside crispy French fries. A popular fast-food dish known for its savory and mildly spicy flavor profile.

menu.name: Drehspieß im Brot
menu.short_description: Rotisserie meat served in bread
menu.full_description: Juicy rotisserie-style meat (likely döner kebab) sliced fresh and served inside a soft bread roll, often accompanied by salad and sauces. A popular quick meal combining tender meat with fresh bread and condiments.
menu.portion_size: One bread roll with meat filling

menu.name: Döner Taschenbrot
menu.short_description: Doner kebab meat served in pocket bread
menu.full_description: Traditional döner kebab meat, thinly sliced from a vertical rotisserie, served inside a pocket-style bread with fresh vegetables and sauces. A staple Turkish-German fast food known for its flavorful and convenient serving style.

menu.name: Kürbissuppe
menu.short_description: Pumpkin soup with pumpkin seed oil and roasted pumpkin seeds
menu.full_description: Creamy pumpkin soup garnished with pumpkin seed oil and roasted pumpkin seeds

menu.short_description: Beef tartare with various pickled vegetables, hard-boiled egg, sea salt butter, and house bread
menu.full_description: Raw beef tartare prepared with allerlei Saures (various pickled vegetables), hard-boiled egg, sea salt butter, and freshly baked house bread

menu.full_description: Traditional Bavarian liver sausage, browned and served with fried egg, potato salad, and Paulaner beer sauce

menu.full_description: Six authentic Nuremberg roasted bratwurst sausages served with sauerkraut, house bread, and mustard

menu.full_description: Traditional Bavarian hot dog in a lye roll topped with roasted and melted onions, mustard cream, and served with potato wedges

menu.full_description: Traditional Bavarian charcuterie board featuring homemade Obatzda, herb quark, assorted cured meats, cold roast, horseradish, garnished with orange slices, roasted pumpkin seeds, fresh herbs, and served with orange-wheat beer dressing

menu.full_description: Traditional Bavarian Sauerbraten, a marinated beef roast slow-cooked to tender perfection, served with homemade brezel (pretzel) dumplings and sweet-sour red cabbage, offering a hearty and flavorful meal typical of Bavarian cuisine.

menu.full_description: Classic Bavarian dessert of thinly rolled pastry filled with spiced apples and raisins, baked until golden and served warm with a smooth vanilla sauce, offering a sweet and comforting finish.

menu.short_description: Roasted quarter duck served with potato dumplings and red cabbage
menu.full_description: A Bavarian specialty featuring a quarter of duck roasted to crispy perfection, accompanied by traditional potato dumplings and sweet-sour red cabbage, delivering a rich and hearty flavor profile.

menu.short_description: Baked cheese dough balls
menu.full_description: Traditional Brazilian baked cheese bread balls, crispy on the outside and soft inside, made from tapioca flour and cheese.

menu.name: Quibe
menu.short_description: Fried beef ball with cheese filling
menu.full_description: Traditional Middle Eastern-inspired Brazilian snack consisting of a fried beef ball stuffed with cheese, crispy on the outside and soft inside.

menu.name: Porção de Mandioca Frita
menu.short_description: Portion of fried manioc with sauce
menu.full_description: Crispy fried manioc (cassava) served with a dipping sauce, a popular Brazilian side or snack.

menu.name: Frango à Passarinho
menu.short_description: Spicy fried chicken pieces with lime
menu.full_description: Brazilian style spicy fried chicken pieces served with lime wedges, crispy and flavorful.

menu.name: Coxinha
menu.short_description: Fried dough pockets filled with chicken
menu.full_description: Brazilian fried dough snacks shaped like chicken drumsticks, filled with shredded chicken and spices.

menu.name: Isca de Peixe ao Molho Coquetel
menu.short_description: Fried fish bites with cocktail sauce
menu.full_description: Breaded and fried fish pieces served with a tangy cocktail sauce (molho tártaro), a popular Brazilian seafood appetizer.

menu.name: Feijoada Completa
menu.short_description: Stew of black beans with pork, rice, fried kale and roasted cassava flour
menu.full_description: Traditional Brazilian black bean stew cooked with various cuts of pork, served with rice, fried kale, and farofa (roasted cassava flour). A hearty and iconic dish.

menu.name: Kabab Tekah
menu.short_description: Grilled chicken breast skewers marinated in saffron
menu.full_description: Tender chicken breast pieces marinated in saffron and grilled to perfection, served as skewers. A signature Afghan grilled dish known for its aromatic flavor and juicy texture.

menu.name: Lammspieße vom Lavastein
menu.short_description: Lamb skewers grilled on lava stone served with grilled vegetables
menu.full_description: Juicy lamb skewers cooked on a lava stone grill, accompanied by a side of grilled seasonal vegetables. This method enhances the flavor and tenderness of the lamb.
menu.special_notes: Grilled on lava stone for enhanced flavor

menu.name: Watan Kabab Teller (for 4 persons)
menu.short_description: Mixed grill platter with various kababs and sides for four people
menu.full_description: A generous platter featuring a variety of grilled meats including lamb skewers, chicken, and beef kababs, served with grilled vegetables, rice, and salad. Ideal for sharing and experiencing a range of Afghan grilled flavors.

menu.name: Kol Washkor
menu.short_description: Pastry with cashew nut filling, baked to golden brown
menu.full_description: A traditional Afghan layered pastry made from many layers of paper-thin dough filled with ground cashews and baked until golden and crisp. A sweet and nutty treat.

menu.name: Kanafeh with Cheese
menu.short_description: Palestinian cheese pastry soaked in sweet syrup
menu.full_description: A traditional Palestinian dessert made with a cheese-filled pastry soaked in a sweet sugar-based syrup, offering a rich and sweet flavor profile.

menu.name: Grill Platter Watan (for two)
menu.short_description: Mixed grill with minced lamb skewers, veal skewers, chicken wings, chicken breast chunks, grilled tomatoes and salad
menu.full_description: A platter designed for two people featuring 2 minced lamb skewers, 2 veal skewers, chicken wings, chicken breast chunks, served with grilled tomatoes, fresh salad, and one side dish. A comprehensive Afghan grill experience.
menu.special_notes: Platter for two, includes side dish

menu.name: Pizza
menu.short_description: Italian-style pizza with various toppings, freshly baked
menu.full_description: A classic Italian pizza, baked to order with a variety of toppings available. The pizza is described as nicely baked and offers all the German standards, including daily specials.
menu.special_notes: Daily pizza special available, can be ordered for takeout

menu.name: Noodles
menu.short_description: Pasta dish, freshly prepared
menu.full_description: Freshly prepared noodles, likely Italian-style pasta, served as a main course. The dish is described as delicious and suitable for both adults and children.

menu.name: Fish
menu.short_description: Fresh fish, tender and well-prepared
menu.full_description: Fresh fish dish, described as tender and flavorful. Likely prepared in a Mediterranean style, suitable for adults and children.

menu.name: Ice Cream
menu.short_description: Classic ice cream, freshly served
menu.full_description: Good quality ice cream, likely served as a dessert. Popular with both locals and families.

menu.name: Cocktails
menu.short_description: Refreshing cocktails, served late into the evening
menu.full_description: A variety of refreshing cocktails available, catering to late-night cravings. The restaurant is open for both lunch and dinner, with cocktail service extending into the evening.

menu.name: Coffee
menu.short_description: Aromatic coffee, freshly brewed
menu.full_description: Aromatic coffee served throughout the day, ideal for a leisurely break or as a complement to a meal.

menu.name: Allgäuer Käsespätzle mit Salat
menu.short_description: Traditional Allgäu cheese spätzle served with a fresh salad
menu.full_description: A classic Bavarian dish featuring soft Swabian egg noodles (Spätzle) mixed with melted Allgäu cheese, topped with crispy fried onions, accompanied by a fresh green salad with light dressing. This dish is a hearty, comforting vegetarian option typical of the Alpine region.
menu.preparation_method: boiled noodles mixed with melted cheese, topped with fried onions
menu.special_notes: Classic Bavarian comfort food, popular vegetarian choice

menu.name: Schinkennudeln (aus Hinterschinken) mit Zwiebeln und Ei
menu.short_description: Pasta with ham, onions, and egg
menu.full_description: A traditional Bavarian dish consisting of pasta noodles tossed with diced hind ham (Hinterschinken), sautéed onions, and scrambled eggs, creating a savory and filling meal with rich flavors.
menu.preparation_method: boiled pasta mixed with sautéed ham and onions, scrambled egg added

menu.name: Knödelgröstel mit Bratenfleisch, Zwiebeln, Ei und Speck
menu.short_description: Pan-fried dumplings with roast meat, onions, egg, and bacon
menu.full_description: A hearty Bavarian dish featuring pan-fried bread dumplings (Knödel) mixed with tender roast meat, caramelized onions, scrambled egg, and crispy bacon pieces, delivering a rich and savory flavor profile typical of traditional Alpine cuisine.
menu.preparation_method: pan-fried mixture of dumplings, meat, onions, egg, and bacon

menu.name: Schweinebraten (Pork Roast)
menu.short_description: Traditional Bavarian pork roast with crispy crackling
menu.full_description: A signature Bavarian dish featuring slow-roasted pork with a crispy crackling skin, served with traditional sides such as dumplings and red cabbage. The pork is sourced primarily from regional straw-fed pigs, ensuring high quality and flavor.
menu.special_notes: Highly recommended, fresh and high-quality pork from straw-fed pigs

menu.name: Spätzle (Swabian Noodles)
menu.short_description: Traditional soft egg noodles from Swabia
menu.full_description: Handmade Swabian egg noodles, boiled and served as a side dish or with cheese (Käsespätzle). A staple in Bavarian and Swabian cuisine, often enjoyed by vegetarians when served plain or with cheese.

menu.name: Pho
menu.short_description: Traditional Vietnamese noodle soup with aromatic broth, rice noodles, herbs, and choice of meat
menu.full_description: Pho is a classic Vietnamese dish featuring a clear, flavorful broth simmered with spices, served with tender rice noodles, fresh herbs like basil and cilantro, lime, and thinly sliced beef or chicken. It is a comforting and aromatic soup, often enjoyed as a main course.

menu.name: Fresh Spring Rolls
menu.short_description: Light Vietnamese rolls with fresh vegetables, herbs, and shrimp or tofu wrapped in rice paper
menu.full_description: Fresh spring rolls are a popular Vietnamese appetizer consisting of rice paper wrapped around fresh herbs, lettuce, vermicelli noodles, and shrimp or tofu. Served with a tangy dipping sauce, they offer a refreshing and healthy start to the meal.

menu.name: Bun Cha
menu.short_description: Grilled pork served with vermicelli noodles, fresh herbs, and dipping sauce
menu.full_description: Bun Cha is a traditional Vietnamese dish featuring grilled fatty pork served over a bed of vermicelli noodles, accompanied by fresh herbs, lettuce, and a sweet and sour dipping sauce. It is a flavorful and balanced dish combining smoky, sweet, and fresh elements.

menu.name: Shrimp Dumplings
menu.short_description: Steamed dumplings filled with shrimp, served as an appetizer
menu.full_description: Delicately steamed shrimp dumplings with a tender wrapper and juicy shrimp filling, served as a starter. The dish is prepared with care to balance the flavors and textures, often accompanied by a dipping sauce.

menu.name: Tuna Dish
menu.short_description: Seared tuna served with vegetables in a flavorful sauce and sticky rice
menu.full_description: A carefully prepared tuna dish featuring seared tuna paired with vegetables cooked in a savory sauce, complemented by sticky rice. The dish balances fresh seafood flavors with rich, umami notes from the sauce.

menu.name: Shaking Beef
menu.short_description: Tender beef steak cubes sautéed with garlic and pepper
menu.full_description: Shaking Beef is a Vietnamese dish consisting of tender cubes of beef steak quickly sautéed with garlic, black pepper, and served with a side of vegetables or rice. The beef is cooked to medium rare to preserve juiciness and flavor.

menu.name: Mango Salad with Duck
menu.short_description: Fresh mango salad topped with tender duck meat
menu.full_description: A refreshing salad combining sweet mango slices with tender, flavorful duck meat, fresh herbs, and a light dressing. This dish balances sweet, savory, and tangy flavors and is a recommended specialty.

menu.name: Chicken Curry
menu.short_description: Tasty chicken curry with rich spices and sauce
menu.full_description: A flavorful chicken curry prepared with a blend of spices and a rich sauce, served with rice or noodles. The dish is well-seasoned and offers a comforting, hearty meal option.

menu.name: Kleiner Gartensalat
menu.short_description: Gemischter Salat der Saison mit Joghurt-Dressing
menu.full_description: Frischer gemischter Salat der Saison, serviert mit einem cremigen Joghurt-Dressing, ideal als leichter Vorspeise oder Beilage.

menu.name: Rumpsteak vom Grill
menu.short_description: Gegrilltes Rumpsteak mit Schmorzwiebeln, Kräuterbutter, Bratkartoffeln und kleinem Gartensalat
menu.full_description: Saftig gegrilltes Rumpsteak, serviert mit karamellisierten Schmorzwiebeln, aromatischer Kräuterbutter, knusprigen Bratkartoffeln und einem kleinen frischen Gartensalat.

menu.name: Brauhaus Burger
menu.short_description: Prime Beef Burger mit Bacon, Zwiebeln, Tomaten, Gurken, Salat und hausgemachter Burgersoße im Brioche-Brötchen, serviert mit Pommes frites
menu.full_description: Saftiger Prime Beef Burger mit knusprigem Bacon, frischen Zwiebeln, Tomaten, Gurken und Salat, verfeinert mit einer hausgemachten Burgersoße, alles im weichen Brioche-Brötchen, dazu knusprige Pommes frites.
menu.special_notes: Option mit extra Käse oder vegetarischem Bratling verfügbar

menu.name: Münchener Schweinsbraten
menu.short_description: Schweinebraten mit Dunkelbiersoße, Kartoffelknödeln und Sauerkraut
menu.full_description: Traditioneller Münchner Schweinebraten, zart geschmort und serviert mit einer kräftigen Dunkelbiersoße, klassischen Kartoffelknödeln und würzigem Sauerkraut.

menu.name: Oktoberfestplatte
menu.short_description: Kleine gegrillte Haxe, paniertes Schweineschnitzel, Kräuterfleischkäse und Weißwurst mit Sauerkraut, Kartoffelknödel, Bratkartoffeln, Biersoße und zweierlei Senf
menu.full_description: Bayerische Spezialitätenplatte mit einer kleinen gegrillten Schweinshaxe, paniertem Schweineschnitzel, würzigem Kräuterfleischkäse und traditioneller Weißwurst, dazu Sauerkraut, Kartoffelknödel, Bratkartoffeln, herzhafte Biersoße und zwei Sorten Senf.

menu.name: Bayern Pfännchen
menu.short_description: Rostbratwurst, Fleischkäse, Bacon und Spiegelei mit Bratkartoffeln und kleinem Gartensalat
menu.full_description: Herzhaftes Pfannengericht mit bayerischer Rostbratwurst, Fleischkäse, knusprigem Bacon und Spiegelei, serviert auf Bratkartoffeln und begleitet von einem kleinen frischen Gartensalat.

menu.name: Winzerpfanne
menu.short_description: Medaillons vom Schweinefilet mit frischen Champignons in Rahmsoße, Kroketten und Butterbohnen im Speckmantel
menu.full_description: Zarte Schweinefiletmedaillons in einer cremigen Rahmsoße mit frischen Champignons, serviert mit knusprigen Kroketten und Butterbohnen, die in Speck gewickelt sind.

menu.name: Biene Maja Teller
menu.short_description: Hausgemachte Spätzle mit Jägersoße
menu.full_description: Frisch zubereitete hausgemachte Spätzle, serviert mit einer herzhaften Jägersoße aus Pilzen und Sahne, ein beliebtes Gericht für Kinder.

menu.name: Donald Duck Teller
menu.short_description: Kleine Rostbratwurst mit Pommes frites und Ketchup
menu.full_description: Kleine bayerische Rostbratwurst, serviert mit knusprigen Pommes frites und Ketchup, ein einfaches und beliebtes Kindergericht.

menu.name: Willi Teller
menu.short_description: Kartoffelkloß mit Bratensoße
menu.full_description: Traditioneller Kartoffelkloß serviert mit einer herzhaften Bratensoße, einfaches und klassisches Gericht für Kinder.

menu.name: Creamy Veal Goulash
menu.short_description: Cremiger Kalbsgulasch mit hausgemachten Spätzle
menu.full_description: Zartes Kalbfleisch in einer cremigen, mild gewürzten Soße, serviert mit frisch hausgemachten Spätzle, ein klassisches bayerisches Gericht.

menu.name: Schnitzel
menu.short_description: Schnitzel mit Kürbiskernkruste, Kartoffel-Gurkensalat und Zitrone
menu.full_description: Knusprig paniertes Schnitzel mit einer speziellen Kürbiskernkruste, serviert mit einem frischen Kartoffel-Gurkensalat und einer Zitronenscheibe zur Abrundung.

menu.name: Chicken-Piccata
menu.short_description: Hähnchen-Piccata mit Paprika-Confit
menu.full_description: Zartes Hähnchenfilet in einer aromatischen Paprika-Confit-Soße, serviert mit Beilagen, typisch italienisch inspiriert.

menu.name: Bio-Roggenlaiberl
menu.short_description: Roggenlaibchen aus Sauerteig und Roggenmehl
menu.full_description: Kleines Roggenbrot aus Bio-Sauerteig und Roggenmehl, traditionell gebacken, ideal als Beilage oder Snack.

menu.name: Bräuhaus – Brezn
menu.short_description: Hefeteigbrezel mit Lauge und Salz
menu.full_description: Traditionelle bayerische Brezel aus Hefeteig, gebadet in Lauge und bestreut mit grobem Salz, frisch gebacken.

menu.name: Obatzda
menu.short_description: Gerupfter Brie mit Radieserl
menu.full_description: Traditioneller bayerischer Käseaufstrich aus gereiftem Brie, fein zerdrückt und mit Radieserl serviert, ideal als Brotzeit.

menu.name: Original Münchner Weißwürste
menu.short_description: Two traditional Bavarian white sausages made from 100% veal, served with sweet Händlmaier mustard and a pretzel
menu.full_description: The Weißwurst is a classic Bavarian delicacy made exclusively from lean veal meat, gently warmed (not boiled) to preserve its delicate texture and flavor. The sausage casing is not eaten but the meat is traditionally sucked out. Served with a freshly baked, crispy-on-the-outside, fluffy-on-the-inside pretzel and sweet mustard from Händlmaier, this dish represents the quintessential Munich breakfast experience.
menu.price: 6.20€ for two sausages, 1.50€ for a pretzel
menu.special_notes: Signature dish, best Weißwurst in Munich, served traditionally with Händlmaier mustard and pretzel. Available even after 12 pm.

menu.name: Regensburger Wurst
menu.short_description: Traditional Bavarian sausage from the house butcher, grilled or cooked
menu.full_description: A classic Bavarian sausage variety made in-house, known for its robust flavor and firm texture. Typically served with mustard and bread or pretzel, it is a popular choice for sausage lovers visiting the Gaststätte Großmarkthalle.
menu.special_notes: House-made sausage from the in-house butcher

menu.name: Debrecziner Wurst
menu.short_description: Spicy Hungarian-style sausage from the house butcher
menu.full_description: A spicy sausage variety inspired by Hungarian Debrecener, made in-house with a blend of pork and spices. It offers a flavorful and slightly piquant taste, ideal for those who enjoy a bit of heat in their sausage.
menu.special_notes: House-made sausage with Hungarian spice influence

menu.name: Pfälzer Wurst
menu.short_description: Traditional sausage from the Palatinate region, house-made
menu.full_description: A regional specialty sausage from the Pfalz area, prepared in-house. Known for its hearty flavor and traditional seasoning, it is a staple on the menu for sausage enthusiasts.

menu.name: Wollwurst
menu.short_description: Traditional Bavarian white sausage variant, house-made
menu.full_description: A type of Bavarian white sausage similar to Weißwurst but with a different texture and preparation style. Made fresh daily in-house, it is a delicacy for sausage lovers seeking variety.

menu.name: Briesmilzwurst
menu.short_description: House-made sausage featuring sweetbread and spleen
menu.full_description: A traditional Bavarian sausage made with a blend of sweetbread (thymus) and spleen, prepared fresh daily in the house butcher's kitchen. This specialty offers a rich and distinctive flavor profile.

menu.name: Kalbsbratwürstl
menu.short_description: House-made veal bratwurst, traditional Bavarian style
menu.full_description: A traditional Bavarian bratwurst made exclusively from veal, prepared fresh daily in the house butcher's kitchen. Known for its delicate flavor and fine texture, it is a popular choice among guests.

menu.name: Wiener Schnitzel mit Kartoffelsalat
menu.short_description: Breaded veal schnitzel served with traditional potato salad
menu.full_description: A classic Austrian dish featuring a thin, breaded and fried veal cutlet served alongside a traditional Bavarian-style potato salad. The schnitzel is crispy on the outside and tender inside, complemented by the tangy and creamy potato salad.

menu.name: Kalbsbeuschel mit Semmelknödel
menu.short_description: Veal lung ragout served with bread dumplings
menu.full_description: A traditional Bavarian dish consisting of a rich ragout made from veal lungs and heart, seasoned with herbs and spices, served with soft bread dumplings (Semmelknödel). This hearty dish is a classic comfort food in the region.

menu.name: Bauerngröstl mit Spiegelei
menu.short_description: Rustic fried potatoes with vegetables and a fried egg on top
menu.full_description: A traditional Bavarian dish featuring pan-fried potatoes mixed with onions, bacon, and herbs, topped with a sunny-side-up fried egg. This hearty dish is a popular comfort food and a staple in Bavarian cuisine.

menu.name: Kaiserschmarrn
menu.short_description: Fluffy shredded pancake dessert with powdered sugar and fruit compote
menu.full_description: A traditional Austrian and Bavarian dessert made from a sweet, fluffy pancake that is shredded into pieces while frying, then sprinkled with powdered sugar and served with a side of fruit compote, typically plum or apple. It is a beloved sweet treat after a hearty meal.
